to the back of the line.

462
00:24:34,342 --> 00:24:37,476
And no more Britney Spears
songs if you want to live.

463
00:24:38,607 --> 00:24:40,566
-I'll go get the drinks.
-Okay.

464
00:24:41,567 --> 00:24:42,742
You happy?

465
00:24:42,785 --> 00:24:44,439
Never happier.

466
00:24:55,363 --> 00:24:56,843
Yes, I understand.

467
00:24:57,713 --> 00:24:58,758
Very sorry to bother you.

468
00:24:59,715 --> 00:25:01,238
Yes.

469
00:25:02,588 --> 00:25:06,592
Wow, so that's 100
phone calls to 100 users,

470
00:25:06,635 --> 00:25:08,332
