00:26:12,266 --> 00:26:13,310
Hey.

492
00:26:14,094 --> 00:26:15,617
Supergirl.

493
00:26:15,661 --> 00:26:19,099
Hi. That's a...
That's a really great costume.

494
00:26:19,142 --> 00:26:20,622
Black.

495
00:26:20,666 --> 00:26:23,103
Now that is cool.

496
00:26:24,670 --> 00:26:26,628
