talking about?

497
00:26:26,672 --> 00:26:29,805
Oh, I love this place.

498
00:26:29,849 --> 00:26:32,112
They just never make the drinks
cold enough, though.

499
00:26:37,683 --> 00:26:39,685
That... How did you...

500
00:26:39,728 --> 00:26:41,687
