to escape reality.

501
00:26:41,730 --> 00:26:43,427
Not have subpar drinks.

502
00:26:43,471 --> 00:26:45,516
This... This isn't real?

503
00:26:45,560 --> 00:26:47,475
What, you think all these
drinks would be on the house?

504
00:26:49,564 --> 00:26:50,521
Are you okay?

505
00:26:51,305 --> 00:26:53,524
This is impossible.

506
00:26:53,568 --> 00:26:55,178
You look like
you are bugging out.

507
00:26:56,919 --> 00:26:57,746
I'll just get someone.

508
00:27:00,749 --> 00:27:03,534
